2001;;The Amati Girls;;American;;Anne De Salvo;;Cloris Leachman, Mercedes Ruehl, Sean Young;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Amati_Girls;;The film centers around an Italian American family of four sisters (Mercedes Ruehl, Dinah Manoff, Sean Young, and Lily Knight) who reside in Philadelphia. After their father's death, in trying to convince their mother (Cloris Leachman) that her life is still worth living, each sister grapples with her own ideas on love, faith, and ultimately, the meaning of life.